Day One sample exercises

  • The office hour is primarily for any questions you might have, but I’ll also work through the following these exercises if you want to give them a try.
  1. Use RStudio to create an RMarkdown file named something like office_01.Rmd
  2. Set up your file with a code chunk that loads the tidyverse, and gapminder packages.
  3. Then use R to draw these plots:
